    "verses": [
      {
        "index": 1398,
        "local_index": 1,
        "narrator_chain": {
          "parts": [
            {
              "kind": "plain",
              "text": "2964 - رَوَى إِسْحَاقُ بْنُ عَمَّارٍ قَالَ"
            }
          ]
        },
        "part_type": "Hadith",
        "path": "/books/man-la-yahduruhu-al-faqih:2:3:113:1",
        "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/34/3/113/1",
        "text": [
          " قَالَ أَبُو عَبْدِ اَللَّهِ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ : «اَلسَّنَةُ اِثْنَا عَشَرَ شَهْراً يُعْتَمَرُ لِكُلِّ شَهْرٍ عُمْرَةٌ »."
        ],
        "translations": {
          "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
            "Hadith.2964 - Ishaq ibn Ammar narrated that Abu Abdullah (as) said:\n\"The year has twelve months, and an Umrah can be performed in each month.\""
          ]
        }
      },
      {
        "index": 1399,
        "local_index": 2,
        "narrator_chain": {
          "parts": [
            {
              "kind": "plain",
              "text": "2965 - وَ "
            },
            {
              "kind": "plain",
              "text": "رَوَى عَلِيُّ بْنُ أَبِي حَمْزَةَ"
            },
            {
              "kind": "plain",
              "text": " عَنْ "
            },
            {
              "kind": "plain",
              "text": "أَبِي اَلْحَسَنِ مُوسَى عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ"
            },
            {
              "kind": "plain",
              "text": " قَالَ"
            }
          ]
        },
        "part_type": "Hadith",
        "path": "/books/man-la-yahduruhu-al-faqih:2:3:113:2",
        "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/34/3/113/2",
        "text": [
          " : «لِكُلِّ شَهْرٍ عُمْرَةٌ» قَالَ فَقُلْتُ لَهُ أَ يَكُونُ أَقَلَّ مِنْ ذَلِكَ قَالَ «لِكُلِّ عَشَرَةِ أَيَّامٍ عُمْرَةٌ»."
        ],
        "translations": {
          "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
            "Hadith.2965 - Ali ibn Abi Hamzah narrated from Abu al-Hasan Musa (as), who said:\n\"There is an Umrah for every month.\"\nI asked him: \"Can it be less than that?\"\nImam (as) said: \"There is an Umrah for every ten days.\""
          ]
        }
      },
      {
        "index": 1400,
        "local_index": 3,
        "narrator_chain": {
          "parts": [
            {
              "kind": "plain",
              "text": "2966 - وَ "
            },
            {
              "kind": "plain",
              "text": "رَوَى أَبَانٌ"
            },
            {
              "kind": "plain",
              "text": " عَنْ "
            },
            {
              "kind": "narrator",
              "path": "/people/narrators/168",
              "text": "أَبِي اَلْجَارُودِ"
            },
            {
              "kind": "plain",
              "text": " عَنْ "
            },
            {
              "kind": "plain",
              "text": "أَحَدِهِمَا عَلَيْهِمَا اَلسَّلاَمُ"
            },
            {
              "kind": "plain",
              "text": " قَالَ"
            }
          ]
        },
        "part_type": "Hadith",
        "path": "/books/man-la-yahduruhu-al-faqih:2:3:113:3",
        "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/34/3/113/3",
        "text": [
          " : سَأَلْتُهُ عَنِ اَلْعُمْرَةِ بَعْدَ اَلْحَجِّ فِي ذِي اَلْحِجَّةِ قَالَ «حَسَنٌ »."
        ],
        "translations": {
          "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
            "Hadith.2966 - Aban narrated from Abu al-Jarud, from one of the Imams (as), who said:\nI asked him about performing Umrah after Hajj in Dhu al-Hijjah.\nImam (as) said: \"It is good.\""
          ]
        }
      }
    ]
  },
